Package: remoter
Type: Package
Title: Remote R: Control a Remote R Session from a Local One
Version: 0.1-1
Description: A set of utilities for controlling a remote R session
    in a client/server pattern.  Network communication is handled
    by the 'ZeroMQ' library.  The client is a custom 'REPL'.
License: BSD 2-clause License + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    pbdZMQ (>= 0.2-1)
Imports:
    stats,
    utils,
    assertthat (>= 0.1)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: Linux, Mac OSX, or Windows.
NeedsCompilation: yes
ByteCompile: yes
Authors@R: c(person("Drew", "Schmidt", role=c("aut", "cre"),
  email="schmidt@math.utk.edu"),
  person("Wei-Chen", "Chen", role="aut"))
Maintainer: Drew Schmidt <schmidt@math.utk.edu>
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
